title: I'm really enjoy middlesticks right now
body:
The roaming ganks, press E to clear a wave, safely farm from tower. CC any junglers who come my way and sustain for days! Whats not to love. 
Middlesticks is love, middlesticks is life

edit: Taken him top lane and support as well..In my last 7 days i'm 7-0 with fiddle almost all pretty good scorings. I think i'm gonna one trick him to gold! or try at least.
